SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT
CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASTOCK) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2))
FROM :1/ACCC
WHERE ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 AND ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 AND ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' AND ACCC_MUTTYPE = :5
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SELECT STCY_CURRENCY, STCY_TOTADEBTNOTESMENTIONED, STCY_TOTACREDNOTESMENTIONED FROM :1/SCHT, :1/STCY WHERE SCHT_ADMNO = :2 AND SCHT_CLNTNO =:3 AND SCHT_BOOKED = 'N' AND STCY_SCHT_NO = SCHT_NO FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
SELECT CAST( SUM(BTCP_AMOUNTCURRH) AS DECIMAL(13,2)) FROM :1/BTCP WHERE BTCP_ADMNO_INITIAL = :2 AND BTCP_CLNTNO_INITIAL = :3 AND BTCP_STATUS <2

Text.val: -- v.LIMITEXCEEDED = V.INVESTMENTCMONC + V.MUTAINVESTMENTC + V.PENDINGADVANCESC - V.MAXFINANCEC

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast(sum(CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON join :1/CLNT on CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3 where CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_MONTH = :5 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':6' for fetch only

select ACCT_CURRENCY, cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC join :1/CLNT on CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3 join :1/ACCT on ACCT_ADMNO = ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO and ACCT_CLNTNO = ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO and ACCT_DATE = ':4' where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' and ACCC_MUTTYPE > 95 group by ACCT_CURRENCY order by ACCT_CURRENCY for fetch only

select CLNA_CURRENCY, cast(sum(CLNA_AADVANCE) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CLNA join :1/CLNT on CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3 where CLNA_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CLNA_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLNA_CLIENTCHARGED ='N' group by CLNA_CURRENCY order by CLNA_CURRENCY for fetch only
